dialogs = Array[String](["Hey, you starting a new business aren't you ? Kind of... unusual one.", "Listen, my banker just turned me down for a loan. I'm behind on my rent, it's urgent !", "I was thinking you could pay her a little visit and sort out my loan… right at her place ! I’m sure her house's walls are covered in overpriced art !", "That'll let me pay back my landlord, and you can pay yourself with what you find there. I promise you won't be disappointed."])
